OL,3,CUrban councils outside London warn
OL,4,CAngela Rayner of financial failure
OL,6,FCouncils in some of the poorest urban
OL,7,Fareas of the country have warned
OL,8,FAngela Rayner that the vast majority
OL,9,Fdo not expect to meet their budget
OL,10,Ftargets in the next financial year.
OL,12,FThe 48 councils outside London, which
OL,13,Fserve 14 million people across
OL,14,Fsouthern ports, the Midlands and the
OL,15,FNorth, have raised the alarm over a
OL,16,Fdramatic drop in confidence in their
OL,17,Ffinancial sustainability, with vital
OL,18,Fservices under threat and reserves
OL,19,Fdwindling.
