OL,3,CUrban councils outside London warn
OL,4,CAngela Rayner of financial failure
OL,6,FThe figures represent a significant
OL,7,Ffall in confidence about the next
OL,8,Ffinancial year after 25% of member
OL,9,Fcouncils said they would meet their
OL,10,Fbudgets in 2024-25.
OL,12,FWhen asked about particular services,
OL,13,F71% said they believe children's
OL,14,Fsocial care services will fall below
OL,15,Frequired delivery standards, including
OL,16,F24% who said service failure was
OL,17,Flikely.
