OL,6,FIn the letter, Sir Stephen said:
OL,7,F"Currently, there is a fundamental
OL,8,Fmismatch between what local
OL,9,Fauthorities are expected to do and the
OL,10,Fresources they have to do it.
OL,12,F"This is pushing local authorities
OL,13,Fcloser to (declaring effective
OL,14,Fbankruptcy) and resulting in
OL,15,Fsignificant cuts to local services."
