OL,4,CAngela Rayner of financial failure
OL,6,FSir Stephen later added: "There is a
OL,7,Fdesperation for council tax
OL,8,Fequalisation in the local government
OL,9,Ffinance settlement and the need for
OL,10,Flonger term certainty to enable
OL,11,Fcouncils to plan better."
