OL,3,CUrban councils outside London warn
OL,4,CAngela Rayner of financial failure
OL,6,FOf the 33 councils which responded to
OL,7,Fthe question, 97% said the 2025-26
OL,8,Flocal government financial settlement
OL,9,Fand spending review were causing
OL,10,Funcertainty for the sector.
OL,12,FSigoma said this is mainly due to
OL,13,Fforecasters predicting a real-terms
OL,14,Fcut to local government funding based
OL,15,Fon existing departmental spending
OL,16,Fplans and the state of the public
OL,17,Ffinances.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
