OL,6,FA total of seven councils have issued
OL,7,Fsection 114 notices declaring
OL,8,Feffective bankruptcy since 2020, with
OL,9,FCroydon issuing three and Nottingham
OL,10,Ftwo.
OL,12,FIn February, the previous government
